metadata.name: Sunset at Venice
metadata.description: As the sun begins to dip below the horizon, the sky above Venice Beach is set ablaze with a breathtaking palette of colors. The vibrant hues of orange, pink, and purple meld seamlessly, painting the heavens with an ethereal glow that reflects off the gentle waves lapping the shore. The iconic palm trees lining the beach cast their long shadows on the warm sand, creating a striking silhouette against the fiery sky.
